																	</h4>
								<div class="postinfo">
									Posted on 2009-01-17@00:11
																																			</div>
																For whatever reason, I cannot login again (emk2203), but my new solution is the script 45lidclosedLVDSoff :<br />
<br />
grep -q -w closed /proc/acpi/button/lid/LID/state && xrandr --output LVDS --off --output TMDS-1 --auto --output VGA --auto --output TV --auto<br />
<br />
Only when the lid is closed when X starts, the internal panel gets switched off and whatever is connected gets autoconfigured.
							</div>
