- my problem is that both laptop monitor and external one are activated at start (and I only need the external one)<br />
- the separate commands of script work in console, however, the script either gets overridden by smthg or doesn't work on restart<br />
- after I manually change monitor settings and log-off, settings get saved on log on, but once I restart the problem comes back<br />
<br />
Happy to hear your thoughts<br />
<br />
I'm using Ubuntu 13.10 Unity.
